12... Bh3 13. Nh4 { leads to massive exchanges after... } 13... Qg4 14. Qxh3
Qxh3 15. gxh3 Bxh4 16. dxe5 Kd7
{ The King is an active piece in the endgame. Use it! } 17. f4 Ke6
{ and its equal as the extra pawn is of no use thanks to the doubled h-pawns. }
