{ The Bishop pair and the passive Knight on e1 gives us good compensation for the pawn deficit. Perry,D @@StartBracket@@2504@@EndBracket@@-Williamson, H @@StartBracket@@2514@@EndBracket@@ ICCF email 2018 }
