{ And next on our agenda is ...Ne7-Ng6 to push the Bishop on h4 to the g3 square. Then, the two Knights will be slowly coming to the f4 square as the f6-Knight will go to h5 once White's Bishop on h4 slips to g3. The two Knights can be super powerful and tricky if you know how to rein them! }
