9. Na4 { Going for the Bishop, but that's not the main point here. } 9... Bb6
10. Nxb6 axb6
{ Though we have lost the Bishop pair, we have got a formidable pawn structure. Next on the cards will be ...h6-Be6 and slowly reroute the f6-Knight to f4 via h5. In fact, Black is more preferable according to the virtual monsters. }
