15. gxh3 Qg6+ 16. Kh2 { 16.Kh1  Qh5  is the point. } 16... Ng4+
{ Throwing in some pieces to open the King. } 17. hxg4 Qxg4 18. e5
{ Only move to survive and to renew communciations but is faced by the perpetual after... }
18... Qh5+ 19. Kg2 Qf3+ { And a draw is unavoidable. } *

