12. Na4 Ba7 { Of course the Bishop has to be preserved. } 13. c4
{ With the intention of c5 and to lock the a7-Bishop but Black has counterplay on the Kingside after... }
13... h5 14. h4 Nxe4
{ and the Knight on e4 creates a disturbance to White's position. } *

