{ Keeping the b2-pawn secure in order to develop the Bishop on c1. Also, the immediate threat is c5 so it is time to take the Rook. }
18... Bxf2+ 19. Nxf2 Re5 20. Be3 Qe6 21. Re1 Re8
{ And there is heavy pressure mounting on the e-file. } *

