7... a6 { Disturbing the Bishop. } 8. Bc4 Na5
{ is the point and the Bishop has no proper square to retreat. White is forced to concede it. }
9. Nc3
{ 9.Ng5  is met by  9...Nxc4  10.Qxc4  Qe7  and the Knight on g5 can be kicked away by ...h6 next. }
9... Nxc4 10. Qxc4 b5 11. Qd3 Be6
{ And Black is in full control. Next on the cards is ...Be7 followed by O-O and ...c6. The order of the moves can be in either order and doesn't make a big difference. }
