[SetUp "1"]

{ Find the right plan here! } 14... Nh5
{ Black gets counterplay as ...Nf4 is coming and he is forced to give the c1-Bishop for the Knight. If he allows the Knight to go to f4, then his position will collapse. }
15. g3 { 15.Nf3  Nf4  is simply equal. } 15... Nf4 16. gxf4 Qg6+
{ is the trick and the e6-Bishop is lost. } *

