[SetUp "1"]

{ Find an unusual idea here which prepares ...c6. } 12... Ke7
{ Renewing the threat of ...c6 as the Bishop on d6 has to be protected. Once again, Black can afford to move the King as his center is solid. As ...c6 is coming, White has to slowly go back with his pieces. }
13. Bc4 Rb8
{ A strong move threatening ...b5 as Bxb5 will lose the piece to ...c6. So, White has to make a decision with his c4-Bishop and cannot create active play. }
*

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
