{ Find the best move. } 13... Nxe4
{ The Knight on e4 and the Bishop on d4 is a menacing combination. Like they say 'beauty and brain is a dangerous combination'. Although hard to equate it in chess terms, let us consider that the Knight is beauty and the Bishop is brain here :@@EndBracket@@. I don't know if from any angle this analogy makes sense, Bazinga! :@@EndBracket@@. }
14. hxg4 Nxf2 { The main point of sacrificing the piece. } 15. Qxe8 Raxe8 16.
Nxf2 Bxf2+ 17. Kh1 { How to continue? } 17... Re4
