{ Find the standard move to kick the bishop on c4. } 8... Na5
{ The standard reaction to hassle the Bishop. } 9. Be2 O-O 10. b4 Nc6 11. b5
Na5
{ Unlike the previous cases where we went with our Knight to b8, here we go forward to a5 as it is important to prevent Bc4 and Ng5 ideas. }
12. Ba3 { Planning Bb4. } 12... c6
{ A multipurpose move. Controls the center, aims for the d5-break, and also secures the Knight on a5. }
13. bxc6 bxc6 14. Rb1 Be6 { Preparing ...Nc4. } *

